uns three state-of- the-art multispecialty dental clinics. All three are located along Al Wasl Road (Jumeirah and Umm Suqeim).</p>\r\n<p>Since its birth in Dubai in 1997, Dr. Michael’s Dental Clinic has built an enviable place in the industry as one of the most trusted dental healthcare providers in the region.</p>\r\n<p>True to its reputation, Dr. Michael’s Dental Clinic has grown thirty times over the last fifteen years with a highly committed team of experts serving more than 40,000 patients to date. We have assembled the finest team of dentists, specialists, dental hygienists and support staff representing General dentistry, Cosmetic dentistry (Aesthetic dentistry), Oral Surgery and Implantology, Orthodontics (braces), Pedodontics (Pediatric dentistry) and Prosthodontics.</p>','about silesia dental','','publish','closed','closed','','about-silesia-dental','','','2016-11-23 09:50:05','2016-11-23 09:50:05','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?page_id=14',0,'page','',0),(15,1,'2016-11-02 11:39:18','2016-11-02 11:39:18','','about silesia dental','','inherit','closed','closed','','14-revision-v1','','','2016-11-02 11:39:18','2016-11-02 11:39:18','',14,'http://silesia.dev/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(16,1,'2016-11-02 11:39:34','2016-11-02 11:39:34','[ank_google_map]','contact us','','publish','closed','closed','','contact-us','','','2016-11-16 11:39:14','2016-11-16 11:39:14','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?page_id=16',0,'page','',0),(17,1,'2016-11-02 11:39:34','2016-11-02 11:39:34','','contact us','','inherit','closed','closed','','16-revision-v1','','','2016-11-02 11:39:34','2016-11-02 11:39:34','',16,'http://silesia.dev/16-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(18,1,'2016-11-02 11:41:37','2016-11-02 11:41:37','','Contact us','','publish','closed','closed','','18','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=18',32,'nav_menu_item','',0),(19,1,'2016-11-02 11:41:37','2016-11-02 11:41:37','','About us','','publish','closed','closed','','19','','','201