ooth surfaces especially. These are more prevalent in areas where the access is hard like crowded teeth, the last molars and between teeth. The longer they stay, the more ill effect they cause in gingiva and periodontium (gums).\r\n\r\nScaling is the first step towards eliminating the present plaque and calculus. It involves using an ultrasound tip with a water jet that helps to dislodge and remove adherent plaque and calculus on tooth surface. This is preferably followed up with surface polishing which removes external stains from the tooth.\r\n<h3 id=\"fluoride-therapy\">FLUORIDE THERAPY</h3>\r\nFluoride helps prevent tooth decay by making the tooth more resistant to acid attacks from plaque bacteria and sugars in the mouth. Fluoride is\r\n\r\nFluoride therapy involves applying fluoride gel to tooth surface for one to four minutes. Its is indicated for infants and children between ages from 6 months upto 15 years to help strengthen and protect the teeth.','maintaining teeth','','inherit','closed','closed','','28-revision-v1','','','2016-11-06 11:38:55','2016-11-06 11:38:55','',28,'http://silesia.dev/28-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(53,1,'2016-11-06 11:47:09','2016-11-06 11:47:09','','Scaling & Polishing','','publish','closed','closed','','scaling-polishing','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=53',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(54,1,'2016-11-06 11:52:14','2016-11-06 11:52:14','','Fuoride Therapy','','publish','closed','closed','','fuoride-therapy','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=54',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(55,1,'2016-11-06 11:52:14','2016-11-06 11:52:14','','Gum Care & Treatments','','publish','closed','closed','','gum-care-treatments','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=55',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(56,1,'2016-11-23 07:59:08','2016-11-23 07:59:08','<h3 id=\"teeth-whitening\">Zoom Teeth Whitening</h3>\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consec