ng teeth','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-autosave-v1','','','2016-11-07 04:51:52','2016-11-07 04:51:52','',42,'http://silesia.dev/42-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(73,1,'2016-11-07 04:54:33','2016-11-07 04:54:33','Teeth that are beyond any repair are to be removed. These leave empty spaces and affect function and esthetics. If the extracted tooth space is left empty long, it leads to bone loss of that area and eruption of the opposing tooth into the space.\r\n\r\nThis is countered by replacing them with viable modern alternatives like dental bridges, crowns and dental implant.\r\n<h3>CROWNS AND BRIDGES</h3>\r\n<p id=\"crowns-bridges\">Crowns and bridges (Fixed Partial Denture) are custom made to fit the dimensions and functionality of the tooth. They come in variations:\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Emax crown (All Porcelain crowns)</strong> These are full porcelain crowns and are strong and provide superiormost esthetics than any other alternatives.\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Zircon crown</strong> These are indicative in areas requiring more strength to withstand heavier forces. The core is buildup with Zirconia (superior strength and white in colour) and is covered with porcelain. The are of excellent esthtic value.\r\n\r\n<strong>3. Porcelain Fused to Metal crown (PFM)</strong> These crowns are made with a metal core which provides strength and covered by porcelain to match tooth colour.<p>','replacing teeth','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2016-11-07 04:54:33','2016-11-07 04:54:33','',42,'http://silesia.dev/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(74,1,'2016-11-07 05:21:00','2016-11-07 05:21:00','','Crowns','','publish','closed','closed','','crowns-bridges','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=74',23,'nav_menu_item','',0),(76,1,'2016-11-07 05:21:00','2016-11-07 05:21:00','','Conventional braces','','publish','closed','closed','','conventional-braces','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=76',16,'nav_menu_item','',0),(77,1,'2016-11-07 05:21:00','2016-11-07 05:21:00','','Self-ligating braces','','publish','closed','closed','','self-ligating-braces','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=77',17,'nav_menu_item','',0),(78,1,'2016-11-07 05:21:00','2016-11-07 05:21:00','','Lingual braces','','publish','closed','closed','','lingual-braces','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=78',18,'nav_menu_item','',0),(79,1,'2016-11-07 05:21:00','2016-11-07 05:21:00','','Invisalign','','publish','closed','closed','','invisalign','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=79',20,'nav_menu_item','',0),(80,1,'2016-11-07 05:21:00','2016-11-07 05:21:00','','Inman Aligner','','publish','closed','closed','','inman-aligner','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=80',21,'nav_menu_item','',0),(81,1,'2016-11-07 05:21:00','2016-11-07 05:21:00','','Orthopedic and Myofunctional','','publish','closed','closed','','orthopedic-and-myofunctional','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=81',19,'nav_menu_item','',0),(82,1,'2016-11-07 05:20:42','2016-11-07 05:20:42','A quality smile adds to a confident smile.\r\n\r\nAn ideally positioned set of teeth exuberates self esteem and self confidence. Also provides better functionality, facilitates better cleaning, reduces tooth decay and in the long run, avoids effects of tooth wear and gum disease caused by malalignment of teeth. Orthodontic treatment allows corrections of all kind of malocclusions such as crowding, spacing, protrusion, crossbite, openbite, deepbite.\r\n\r\nGetting Orthodontic treatment done during childhood or teen age is always faster and more sustaining. Growth can be utilized at this age to rectify many problems at their onset. Habits such as thumbsucking and tongue thrusting can have deterrent effect on teeth and jaw. These are best corrected at an early age using habit breaking and myofunctional appliances.\r\n\r\nHowever, there is no particular age to perfect your smile. Many adults are aware of their smile imperfections and opt to get treated Orthodonitcally to successfully attain beautiful smiles. TMJ associated Issues (TMD) and sleep apnoea are also extensively treated Orthodontically. With\r\n\r\nWith use of modern methods and technology, our Specialist Orthodontist is able to provide the best braces in Dubai with a wide range of options that best suits your treatment and one that blends into your lifestyle with esthetics and convenience.\r\n\r\n<strong id=\"conventional-braces\">1. Conventional braces Metal ceramic:</strong>  This has been the backbone of Orthodontic treatment and are the most used modality. Modern brackets are more smaller, less noticeable and are better tolerated by cheek and lips. Both metal and ceramic provide same treatment time, although the ceramic braces are preferred by many for their esthetic appeal.\r\n\r\n<strong id=\"selfligating-braces\">2. Self-ligating braces:</strong>  Damon self ligating brackets is the most modern system that uses lesser forces to provide more frictionless movement of teeth, when compared with traditional braces. The self ligation provides lesser friction between wire and bracket, allowing a slide movement that has lesser pressure on teeth and shortens the treatment time. These are available in metal and ceramic.\r\n\r\n<strong id=\"invisible-braces\">3. Lingual (invisible) braces:</strong>  They are similar to traditional braces, but the brackets and wires are attached behind the teeth, making it invisible. Highly recommended for individuals who prefer the treatment to remain inconspicuous.\r\n\r\n<strong id=\"invisalign\">4. Invisalign:</strong>  With nano and 3D printing technology advancing, it has provided a new array of treatment choices into Orthodontics. This system has a set of sequential removable clear aligners that are custom made for each individual designed to move their teeth. The aligners are changed into a newer set every 2 weeks providing new activation. These are convenient as they are almost invisible and are removed while eating. They are the perfect solution for people who find the look and feel of the traditional braces unappealing and discomforting.\r\n\r\n<strong id=\"inman-aligner\">5. Inman aligner:</strong>  This is a removable type of solution to correct mild to moderate malalignment and crowding. Although limited to correction range, the advantage is that the treatment is very short.\r\n\r\n<strong id=\"orthopedic-myofunctional\">6. Habit breaking and myofunctional appliances:</strong>  These are primarily for children and adolescent patients who require early intervention to correct prolonged habits and developing deformities in teeth and jaw bones.Prolonged Thumbsucking and tongue thrusting are common habits that cause effect on teeth and jaw. Myofuntional appliances are used for correcting bony defect such as protruding jaw and also in correction of short lower jaw.','Orthodontics','','inherit','closed','closed','','34-revision-v1','','','2016-11-07 05:20:42','2016-11-07 05:20:42','',34,'http://silesia.dev/34-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(83,1,'2016-11-07 05:41:56','2016-11-07 05:41:56','','Bridges','','publish','closed','closed','','bridges','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=83',24,'nav_menu_item','',0),(85,1,'2016-11-07 09:04:37','2016-11-07 09:04:37','','Dentures','','publish','closed','closed','','dentures','','','2016-11-20 12:03:26','2016-11-20 12:03:26','',0,'http://silesia.dev/?p=85',25,'nav_menu_item','',0),(87,1,'2016-11-07 10:24:16','2016-11-07 10:24:16','Your teeth are an extension if your personal health and hygiene. Its essential to make the best routines and habits to keep them top notch and healthy.\r\n<h3>SCALING &amp; POLISHING</h3>\r\n[column lg=\"8\" md=\"12\" sm=\"12\" xs=\"12\" ]\r\